# Criando a VLAN no mk1:

# O procedimento é o mesmo para cada VLAN..

    Interfaces > VLAN > Add

        New Interface
        
            General

                Name: vlan10-eth2

                VLAN ID: 10

# Interface de saída para o outro mk (TAGGED):
                
                Interface: eth2-mk2

# A mesma interface de saída/transporte pode ser usada para quantas VLANs desejar!

# Criar a VLAN nos dois mk, atentar a interface de saída!

# Definindo o IP de cada interface VLAN:

    IP > Addresses

        Addresses List > Add

            New Address

                Address: 10.10.10.1/24

                Interface: vlan10-eth2

                    IP > Addresses

# Definindo os servidores dhcp para cada VLAN:

    IP > DHCP SERVER > DHCP Setup

# No mk2:

    IP > Addresses

        Addresses List > Add

            New Address

                Address: 10.10.10.2/24

                Interface: vlan10-eth2

# Criar a bridge:

    Bridge > Bridge > Add

        General

            Name: bridge-vlan10

# Adicionando a interface UNTAGGED e VLAN na bridge:

    Bridge > Ports > Add

        New Bridge Port

            Interface: eth1-pc10

            Bridge: bridge-vlan10

    Bridge > Ports > Add

        New Bridge Port

            Interface: vlan10-eth2

            Bridge: bridge-vlan10

    Bridge > Ports > Add

        New Bridge Port

            Interface: eth2-pc20

            Bridge: bridge-vlan20

    Bridge > Ports > Add

        New Bridge Port

            Interface: VLAN20

            Bridge: bridge-vlan20
